; Test full commodity comparison path with multiple annotation attributes
; Covers commodity.cc compare_by_commodity with prices, dates, and tags
; including paths 391-399 (annotated vs non-annotated), 405-411
; (price vs no-price), 445-467 (date comparison)

2024/01/01 Buy with full annotations
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL {$150.00} [2024/01/01] (lot-a)
    Assets:Cash        $-1500.00

2024/01/02 Buy with different date and tag
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {$150.00} [2024/06/15] (lot-b)
    Assets:Cash         $-750.00

2024/01/03 Buy with same price, no date, no tag
    Assets:Brokerage    3 AAPL {$150.00}
    Assets:Cash         $-450.00

test bal --no-total --lots Brokerage
    3 AAPL {$150.00}
10 AAPL {$150.00} [2024/01/01] (lot-a)
5 AAPL {$150.00} [2024/06/15] (lot-b)  Assets:Brokerage
end test
